                                "text": "\n\n            Bug ID: 19013\n           Summary: Incorrect computations in mood.test (and ansari.test?)\n                    in case of ties\n           Product: R\n           Version: R 4.5.x\n          Hardware: All\n                OS: All\n            Status: UNCONFIRMED\n          Severity: normal\n          Priority: P5\n         Component: Accuracy\n          Assignee: "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "link",
